%md
# Preprocessing
## process list
- Illuminance scale
- time aggregation

paragraphs.title: init dataset + scale
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
import numpy as np
import random
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense
from pyspark.sql import Row
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_month, udf_weather, udf_30min


udf_scaler = udf(lambda i: i/10000, DoubleType())

# 1-1. 데이터셋 생성하기
sz = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///sun/angle_calc.parquet')
nt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/nt_srs.parquet')\
                .where('date > "2017-04-11"')
uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')
aday = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/available_days.parquet')

spdf = nt.join(uv, ['date', 'time'])\
         .join(sz, ['date', 'time'])\
         .where('illum > 0 and uvi > 0 and uvi < 14')\
         .select('date', 'time', 'illum', 'uvi', 'solar_zenith')\
         .withColumn('time', udf_30min('time'))\
         .groupby('date', 'time').avg('illum', 'solar_zenith', 'uvi')\
         .withColumnRenamed('avg(illum)', 'illum')\
         .withColumnRenamed('avg(solar_zenith)', 'solar_zenith')\
         .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'uvi')\
         .withColumn('illum_s', udf_scaler('illum'))

# 랜덤시드 고정시키기
np.random.seed(5)

paragraphs.title: new dataset
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType, DoubleType
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_month, udf_weather
from pyspark.ml.regression import LinearRegression
from pyspark.ml.evaluation import RegressionEvaluator
from pyspark.ml.feature import VectorAssembler
from pyspark.ml.pipeline import Pipeline, PipelineModel

# ds_tt = spdf.select('date', 'time', 'illum', 'illum_s', 'solar_zenith', 'uvi')

assembler = VectorAssembler(inputCols=['illum_s', 'solar_zenith'],
                            outputCol='features')

asm_train = assembler.transform(spdf_train_b)
asm_test = assembler.transform(spdf_test)

# ds_train, ds_test = asm_ds.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 2)

lr = LinearRegression(maxIter=300, regParam=0.3, elasticNetParam=0.8,
                      featuresCol='features', labelCol='uvi',
                      predictionCol='predic_uvi')
lrModel = lr.fit(asm_train)

coef = float(lrModel.coefficients[0])
intcpt = float(lrModel.intercept)
smry = lrModel.summary
print('train> R2: %.4f, RMSE: %.4f' % (smry.r2, smry.rootMeanSquaredError))

# test dataset
ds_res_test = lrModel.transform(asm_test)
ds_res_test.cache()
# ds_res_test.show()

# evaluate
evaluator = RegressionEvaluator(labelCol='uvi', predictionCol='predic_uvi')
rmse = evaluator.evaluate(ds_res_test)
mse = evaluator.setMetricName('mse').evaluate(ds_res_test)
r2 = evaluator.setMetricName('r2').evaluate(ds_res_test)
mae = evaluator.setMetricName('mae').evaluate(ds_res_test)
print("test> r2:%.4f, mae:%.4f, mse:%.4f, rmse:%.4f" % (r2, mae, mse, rmse))

# pipeline
# pipeline_exp = Pipeline(stages=[assembler, lr])
# plmodel_exp = pipeline_exp.fit(spdf)  # input dataset before assembling

x = list(map(lambda r: r['illum'], ds_res_test.select('illum').collect()))

yf = list(map(lambda r: r['predic_uvi'], ds_res_test.select('predic_uvi').collect()))

# plotting

ax.legend(fontsize=18)
plt.show()

paragraphs.title: construct model, FIT!!!!!!!
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense
from keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping

# 2. 모델 구성하기
hidden_layers=2
nodes=20
epochs=300
batch_size=64

model = Sequential()
model.add(Dense(nodes, input_dim=2, activation='relu'))
for i in range(hidden_layers-1):
    print('>> hidden layer added:', i+2)
    model.add(Dense(nodes, activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(1))

# 3. 모델 학습과정 설정하기
model.compile(optimizer='rmsprop', loss='mae', metrics=['mse'])

# 4. 모델 학습시키기
early_stopping = EarlyStopping(patience=20)
hist = model.fit(x_train, y_train, epochs=epochs,
                 batch_size=batch_size,
                 validation_data=(x_val, y_val),
                 callbacks=[early_stopping])

%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_30min, udf_10min

df = spdf_eval.select('time', 'uvi', 'uvi_pred')\
              .withColumn('time', udf_10min('time'))\
              .groupby('time').avg('uvi', 'uvi_pred').sort('time')\
              .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'UVI_CAS')\
              .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi_pred)', 'UVI_Estimated')
df.createOrReplaceTempView('df')
